{"hits": {"hits": [{"created": "2024-01-01T22:37:39.624389+00:00", "modified": "2024-01-01T22:37:39.981051+00:00", "id": 10449707, "conceptrecid": "10449706", "doi": "10.5281/zenodo.10449707", "conceptdoi": "10.5281/zenodo.10449706", "doi_url": "https://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10449707", "metadata": {"title": "iPSCviRPEcounts", "doi": "10.5281/zenodo.10449707", "publication_date": "2024-01-01", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Delphi", "affiliation": null}], "resource_type": {"title": "Dataset", "type": "dataset"}, "license": {"id": "cc-by-4.0"}, "relations": {"version": [{"index": 0, "is_last": true, "parent": {"pid_type": "recid", "pid_value": "10449706"}}]}}, "title": "iPSCviRPEcounts", "links": {"self": "https://zenodo.org/api/records/10449707", "self_html": "https://zenodo.org/records/10449707", "preview_html": "https://zenodo.org/records/10449707?preview=1", "doi": "https://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10449707", "self_doi": "https://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10449707", "self_doi_html": "https://zenodo.org/doi/10.5281/zenodo.10449707", "reserve_doi": "https://zenodo.org/api/records/10449707/draft/pids/doi", "parent": "https://zenodo.org/api/records/10449706", "parent_html": "https://zenodo.org/records/10449706", "parent_doi": "https://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10449706", "parent_doi_html": "https://zenodo.org/doi/10.5281/zenodo.10449706", "self_iiif_manifest": "https://zenodo.org/api/iiif/record:10449707/manifest", "self_iiif_sequence": "https://zenodo.org/api/iiif/record:10449707/sequence/default", "files": "https://zenodo.org/api/records/10449707/files", "media_files": "https://zenodo.org/api/records/10449707/media-files", "archive": "https://zenodo.org/api/records/10449707/files-archive", "archive_media": "https://zenodo.org/api/records/10449707/media-files-archive", "latest": "https://zenodo.org/api/records/10449707/versions/latest", "latest_html": "https://zenodo.org/records/10449707/latest", "versions": "https://zenodo.org/api/records/10449707/versions", "draft": "https://zenodo.org/api/records/10449707/draft", "access_links": "https://zenodo.org/api/records/10449707/access/links", "access_grants": "https://zenodo.org/api/records/10449707/access/grants", "access_users": "https://zenodo.org/api/records/10449707/access/users", "access_request": "https://zenodo.org/api/records/10449707/access/request", "access": "https://zenodo.org/api/records/10449707/access", "communities": "https://zenodo.org/api/records/10449707/communities", "communities-suggestions": "https://zenodo.org/api/records/10449707/communities-suggestions", "request_deletion": "https://zenodo.org/api/records/10449707/request-deletion", "file_modification": "https://zenodo.org/api/records/10449707/file-modification", "quota_increase": "https://zenodo.org/api/records/10449707/quota-increase", "requests": "https://zenodo.org/api/records/10449707/requests"}, "updated": "2024-01-01T22:37:39.981051+00:00", "recid": "10449707", "revision": 4, "files": [], "swh": null, "owners": [{"id": "1048243"}], "status": "published", "stats": {"downloads": 0, "unique_downloads": 0, "views": 24, "unique_views": 24, "version_downloads": 0, "version_unique_downloads": 0, "version_unique_views": 24, "version_views": 24}, "state": "done", "submitted": true}, {"created": "2021-07-06T14:49:48.625434+00:00", "modified": "2021-07-07T01:48:15.149630+00:00", "id": 5075944, "conceptrecid": "5075943", "doi": "10.5281/zenodo.5075944", "conceptdoi": "10.5281/zenodo.5075943", "doi_url": "https://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5075944", "metadata": {"title": "Delphi method scoring for consensus statement for occupational heat safety", "doi": "10.5281/zenodo.5075944", "publication_date": "2021-07-06", "description": "<p>The purpose of this consensus document was to develop feasible, evidence-based occupational heat safety recommendations to protect U.S workers that experience heat stress. Heat safety recommendations were created to protect worker health and to avoid productivity losses associated with occupational heat stress. Recommendations were tailored to be utilized by safety managers, industrial hygienists, and the employers who bear responsibility for implementing heat safety plans. An interdisciplinary roundtable comprised of 51 experts was assembled to create a narrative review summarizing current data and gaps in knowledge within eight heat safety topics: (1) heat hygiene, (2) hydration, (3) heat acclimatization, (4) environmental monitoring, (5) physiological monitoring, (6) body cooling, (7) textiles and personal protective gear, and (8) emergency action plan implementation. The consensus-based recommendations for each topic were created using the Delphi method and evaluated based on scientific evidence, feasibility and clarity. The current document presents 40 occupational heat safety recommendations across all eight topics. Establishing these recommendations will help organizations and employers create effective heat safety plans for their workplace, address factors that limit the implementation of heat safety best-practices and protect worker health and productivity.</p>", "access_right": "open", "creators": [{"name": "Margaret Morrissey", "affiliation": "University of Connecticut"}], "version": "1", "resource_type": {"title": "Dataset", "type": "dataset"}, "journal": {"title": "GeoHealth"}, "license": {"id": "cc-by-4.0"}, "relations": {"version": [{"index": 0, "is_last": true, "parent": {"pid_type": "recid", "pid_value": "5075943"}}]}, "notes": "Consensus Document for Occupational Heat Safety: Delphi Scoring"}, "title": "Delphi method scoring for consensus statement for occupational heat safety", "links": {"self": "https://zenodo.org/api/records/5075944", "self_html": "https://zenodo.org/records/5075944", "preview_html": "https://zenodo.org/records/5075944?preview=1", "doi": "https://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5075944", "self_doi": "https://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5075944", "self_doi_html": "https://zenodo.org/doi/10.5281/zenodo.5075944", "reserve_doi": "https://zenodo.org/api/records/5075944/draft/pids/doi", "parent": "https://zenodo.org/api/records/5075943", "parent_html": "https://zenodo.org/records/5075943", "parent_doi": "https://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5075943", "parent_doi_html": "https://zenodo.org/doi/10.5281/zenodo.5075943", "self_iiif_manifest": "https://zenodo.org/api/iiif/record:5075944/manifest", "self_iiif_sequence": "https://zenodo.org/api/iiif/record:5075944/sequence/default", "files": "https://zenodo.org/api/records/5075944/files", "media_files": "https://zenodo.org/api/records/5075944/media-files", "archive": "https://zenodo.org/api/records/5075944/files-archive", "archive_media": "https://zenodo.org/api/records/5075944/media-files-archive", "latest": "https://zenodo.org/api/records/5075944/versions/latest", "latest_html": "https://zenodo.org/records/5075944/latest", "versions": "https://zenodo.org/api/records/5075944/versions", "draft": "https://zenodo.org/api/records/5075944/draft", "access_links": "https://zenodo.org/api/records/5075944/access/links", "access_grants": "https://zenodo.org/api/records/5075944/access/grants", "access_users": "https://zenodo.org/api/records/5075944/access/users", "access_request": "https://zenodo.org/api/records/5075944/access/request", "access": "https://zenodo.org/api/records/5075944/access", "communities": "https://zenodo.org/api/records/5075944/communities", "communities-suggestions": "https://zenodo.org/api/records/5075944/communities-suggestions", "request_deletion": "https://zenodo.org/api/records/5075944/request-deletion", "file_modification": "https://zenodo.org/api/records/5075944/file-modification", "quota_increase": "https://zenodo.org/api/records/5075944/quota-increase", "requests": "https://zenodo.org/api/records/5075944/requests"}, "updated": "2021-07-07T01:48:15.149630+00:00", "recid": "5075944", "revision": 2, "files": [{"id": "66d202e6-7837-4d70-b172-a8204f5e14dc", "key": "Round 2_ Recommendations Scoring .docx", "size": 69312, "checksum": "md5:b4459930065dd6ade18c80b863b12b55", "links": {"self": "https://zenodo.org/api/records/5075944/files/Round%202_%20Recommendations%20Scoring%20.docx/content"}}, {"id": "ca362d66-fafa-4df4-b773-58029458dab6", "key": "OriginalRound1_2.9..2021.docx", "size": 125923, "checksum": "md5:ff60c9e83013474f6e92246837d730b8", "links": {"self": "https://zenodo.org/api/records/5075944/files/OriginalRound1_2.9..2021.docx/content"}}], "swh": null, "owners": [{"id": "240580"}], "status": "published", "stats": {"downloads": 57, "unique_downloads": 55, "views": 415, "unique_views": 411, "version_downloads": 57, "version_unique_downloads": 55, "version_unique_views": 408, "version_views": 412}, "state": "done", "submitted": true}, {"created": "2025-12-10T07:21:24.685535+00:00", "modified": "2025-12-10T07:21:26.188712+00:00", "id": 17876108, "conceptrecid": "17876106", "doi": "10.5281/zenodo.17876108", "conceptdoi": "10.5281/zenodo.17876106", "doi_url": "https://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.17876108", "metadata": {"title": "A Delphi Study for an AI Framework in Biomedical Education and Academics Researchers", "doi": "10.5281/zenodo.17876108", "publication_date": "2025-12-10", "description": "<h3><strong>Study Context</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Type of Study:</strong> Delphi method (iterative consensus-building process).</li>\n<li><strong>Location:</strong> Spain.</li>\n<li><strong>Language of Data:</strong> Spanish.</li>\n<li><strong>Rounds:</strong> 2 rounds of questionnaires.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n<h3><strong>Data Sources</strong></h3>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p><strong>CSV Files from REDCap (3 files):</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>File 1:</strong>&nbsp;<em>Round1 Responses</em></li>\n<li><strong>File 2:</strong> <em>Closing remarks from questionnaire 1</em></li>\n<li><strong>File 3:</strong> <em>Round 2 Responses</em><br>Contains updated ratings after feedback, plus any additional comments.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Common Structure in CSVs:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Columns: <code>participant_id</code>, <code>item_id</code>, <code>score</code> (Likert scale), <code>comment</code> (free text), <code>timestamp</code>.</li>\n<li>Rows: Each participant&rsquo;s response per item.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ol>\n\n\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Codebooks (2 documents):</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Round 1 Codebook:</strong><br>Lists all items/questions presented in the first round, their identifiers, and definitions.</li>\n<li><strong>Round 2 Codebook:</strong><br>Includes revised items based on Round 1 feedback, plus any new items added.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Codebook Structure:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Columns: <code>item_id</code>, <code>item_text</code> (in Spanish), <code>domain</code> (e.g., clinical, organizational), <code>notes</code>.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ol>\n\n\n<h3><strong>Data Characteristics</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Quantitative Data:</strong><br>Likert-scale ratings (e.g., 1&ndash;9 for importance or agreement).</li>\n<li><strong>Qualitative Data:</strong><br>Open-ended comments in Spanish, providing reasoning or suggestions.</li>\n<li><strong>Panel Size:</strong><br>Number of participants (from demographic file).</li>\n<li><strong>Iteration:</strong><br>Round 2 responses show convergence or divergence compared to Round 1.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>study funded by SEDEM (Spanish Society for Medical Education. Grant info: <a href=\"https://sedem.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Becas-a-Proyectos-de-Investigacion-SEDEM-2023.pdf\">Becas-a-Proyectos-de-Investigacion-SEDEM-2023.pdf</a>)</strong></p>", "access_right": "open", "creators": [{"name": "Gonzalez-Soltero, Rocio", "affiliation": "Universidad Europea de Madrid", "orcid": "0000-0001-9799-0570"}], "resource_type": {"title": "Dataset", "type": "dataset"}, "license": {"id": "cc-by-4.0"}, "relations": {"version": [{"index": 0, "is_last": true, "parent": {"pid_type": "recid", "pid_value": "17876106"}}]}}, "title": "A Delphi Study for an AI Framework in Biomedical Education and Academics Researchers", "links": {"self": "https://zenodo.org/api/records/17876108", "self_html": "https://zenodo.org/records/17876108", "preview_html": "https://zenodo.org/records/17876108?preview=1", "doi": "https://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.17876108", "self_doi": "https://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.17876108", "self_doi_html": "https://zenodo.org/doi/10.5281/zenodo.17876108", "reserve_doi": "https://zenodo.org/api/records/17876108/draft/pids/doi", "parent": "https://zenodo.org/api/records/17876106", "parent_html": "https://zenodo.org/records/17876106", "parent_doi": "https://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.17876106", "parent_doi_html": "https://zenodo.org/doi/10.5281/zenodo.17876106", "self_iiif_manifest": "https://zenodo.org/api/iiif/record:17876108/manifest", "self_iiif_sequence": "https://zenodo.org/api/iiif/record:17876108/sequence/default", "files": "https://zenodo.org/api/records/17876108/files", "media_files": "https://zenodo.org/api/records/17876108/media-files", "thumbnails": {"10": "https://zenodo.org/api/iiif/record:17876108:code%20book_Delphi.pdf/full/%5E10,/0/default.jpg", "50": "https://zenodo.org/api/iiif/record:17876108:code%20book_Delphi.pdf/full/%5E50,/0/default.jpg", "100": "https://zenodo.org/api/iiif/record:17876108:code%20book_Delphi.pdf/full/%5E100,/0/default.jpg", "250": "https://zenodo.org/api/iiif/record:17876108:code%20book_Delphi.pdf/full/%5E250,/0/default.jpg", "750": "https://zenodo.org/api/iiif/record:17876108:code%20book_Delphi.pdf/full/%5E750,/0/default.jpg", "1200": "https://zenodo.org/api/iiif/record:17876108:code%20book_Delphi.pdf/full/%5E1200,/0/default.jpg"}, "archive": "https://zenodo.org/api/records/17876108/files-archive", "archive_media": "https://zenodo.org/api/records/17876108/media-files-archive", "latest": "https://zenodo.org/api/records/17876108/versions/latest", "latest_html": "https://zenodo.org/records/17876108/latest", "versions": "https://zenodo.org/api/records/17876108/versions", "draft": "https://zenodo.org/api/records/17876108/draft", "access_links": "https://zenodo.org/api/records/17876108/access/links", "access_grants": "https://zenodo.org/api/records/17876108/access/grants", "access_users": "https://zenodo.org/api/records/17876108/access/users", "access_request": "https://zenodo.org/api/records/17876108/access/request", "access": "https://zenodo.org/api/records/17876108/access", "communities": "https://zenodo.org/api/records/17876108/communities", "communities-suggestions": "https://zenodo.org/api/records/17876108/communities-suggestions", "request_deletion": "https://zenodo.org/api/records/17876108/request-deletion", "file_modification": "https://zenodo.org/api/records/17876108/file-modification", "quota_increase": "https://zenodo.org/api/records/17876108/quota-increase", "requests": "https://zenodo.org/api/records/17876108/requests"}, "updated": "2025-12-10T07:21:26.188712+00:00", "recid": "17876108", "revision": 4, "files": [{"id": "eea4997c-a3a0-448b-bdf4-2ffc7957b34f", "key": "code book_Delphi.pdf", "size": 899132, "checksum": "md5:4e309a9fa9e2896a99b3d891d5d834ec", "links": {"self": "https://zenodo.org/api/records/17876108/files/code%20book_Delphi.pdf/content"}}, {"id": "84130e12-184f-41ef-a70c-31e75e570f44", "key": "DELPHI_DATA_2024-01-15_1153_anonimizada.csv", "size": 1600, "checksum": "md5:69623c81a5622ba81b36e68863453437", "links": {"self": "https://zenodo.org/api/records/17876108/files/DELPHI_DATA_2024-01-15_1153_anonimizada.csv/content"}}, {"id": "30cf21b2-40f7-47c4-966b-40686a15abc8", "key": "DELPHIFASEII_ Datos separados.xlsx", "size": 17179, "checksum": "md5:a52d83c7c1be47af25bd343a56099a54", "links": {"self": "https://zenodo.org/api/records/17876108/files/DELPHIFASEII_%20Datos%20separados.xlsx/content"}}, {"id": "c0ce9e96-086e-439e-b449-97f96ffc2906", "key": "code book questionnaire 2.pdf", "size": 364786, "checksum": "md5:1523b8b0e091d2065ccc131c7289330c", "links": {"self": "https://zenodo.org/api/records/17876108/files/code%20book%20questionnaire%202.pdf/content"}}, {"id": "5242840c-ee9a-4b23-a5d5-ac5e59e8f9c1", "key": "PRUEBAROCIO_DATA_2024-02-02_1649_cuestionario 2.csv", "size": 3194, "checksum": "md5:7bd5c3d8374f2f03205e077690cb0044", "links": {"self": "https://zenodo.org/api/records/17876108/files/PRUEBAROCIO_DATA_2024-02-02_1649_cuestionario%202.csv/content"}}], "swh": null, "owners": [{"id": "63660"}], "status": "published", "stats": {"downloads": 100, "unique_downloads": 90, "views": 69, "unique_views": 64, "version_downloads": 100, "version_unique_downloads": 90, "version_unique_views": 64, "version_views": 69}, "state": "done", "submitted": true}, {"created": "2021-06-22T15:20:23.311178+00:00", "modified": "2022-05-29T01:57:32.581294+00:00", "id": 5013730, "conceptrecid": "5013729", "doi": "10.5061/dryad.86t23", "doi_url": "https://doi.org/10.5061/dryad.86t23", "metadata": {"title": "Data from: Exploring health literacy competencies toward patient education program for Chinese-speaking healthcare professionals: a Delphi study", "doi": "10.5061/dryad.86t23", "publication_date": "2016-09-21", "description": "Objectives: To achieve consensus on a set of competencies in health literacy practice based on a literature review and expert consultation. Setting: Hospitals and community health centres in Taiwan. Method: A 2-stage modified Delphi study involving a literature review was conducted, followed by qualitative interviews and 3 rounds of email-based data collection over a 3-month period in 2011. Participants: 15 Chinese healthcare practitioners with more than 6\u2005months' experience in patient education were interviewed to collect data on health literacy practice. 24 experts (12 academic scholars in health literacy and 12 professionals with training related to health literacy practice) were invited to participate in the Delphi process. Results: Qualitative data from the interviews were analysed and summarised to form 99 competency items for health literacy practice, which were categorised into 5 domains of health literacy practice including those pertaining to knowledge and skills. Consensus was reached on 92 of 99 competencies, using a modified Delphi technique. Conclusions: The 92 competencies in health literacy practice embraced core components of patient education in the Chinese healthcare profession.", "access_right": "open", "creators": [{"name": "Chang, Li-Chun", "affiliation": "Chang Gung University of Science and Technology"}, {"name": "Chen, Yu-Chi", "affiliation": "National Yang Ming University"}, {"name": "Wu, Fei Ling", "affiliation": "Chang Gung University of Science and Technology"}, {"name": "Liao, Li-Ling", "affiliation": "I-Shou University"}], "keywords": ["health profession", "health literacy", "competencies", "Delphi method"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "10.1136/bmjopen-2016-011772", "relation": "isCitedBy", "scheme": "doi"}], "resource_type": {"title": "Dataset", "type": "dataset"}, "license": {"id": "cc-zero"}, "communities": [{"id": "dryad"}], "relations": {"version": [{"index": 0, "is_last": true, "parent": {"pid_type": "recid", "pid_value": "5013729"}}]}, "notes": "<div class=\"o-metadata__file-usage-entry\">Description of Delphi results<div class=\"o-metadata__file-description\">This file contains the description of the Delphi results in Chinese and English.</div><div class=\"o-metadata__file-name\">generated_6210827.doc<br></div></div>"}, "title": "Data from: Exploring health literacy competencies toward patient education program for Chinese-speaking healthcare professionals: a Delphi study", "links": {"self": "https://zenodo.org/api/records/5013730", "self_html": "https://zenodo.org/records/5013730", "preview_html": "https://zenodo.org/records/5013730?preview=1", "doi": "https://doi.org/10.5061/dryad.86t23", "self_doi": "https://doi.org/10.5061/dryad.86t23", "self_doi_html": "https://zenodo.org/doi/10.5061/dryad.86t23", "reserve_doi": "https://zenodo.org/api/records/5013730/draft/pids/doi", "parent": "https://zenodo.org/api/records/5013729", "parent_html": "http